OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F152A1784142692
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNEWSCHundreds of jobs to go at BBC News
OL,4,Cin first stage of major cost-cutting
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe restructuring is the BBC's largest
OL,8,Fin over a decade and comes at a
OL,9,Fdelicate moment for new
OL,10,Fdirector-general Matt Brittin, the
OL,11,Fex-Google executive now tasked with
OL,12,Fresetting the broadcaster's finances.
OL,14,FHe has acknowledged tough choices ahead
OL,15,Fwhile cautioning against "salami
OL,16,Fslicing" teams.
OL,18,FAlongside recruitment and travel
OL,19,Ffreezes, Brittin must fund digital
OL,20,Finvestment in iPlayer and YouTube to
OL,21,Freach younger viewers.
OL,23,EPub: 15-Jun-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
