OL,3,GNEWSCHundreds of jobs to go at BBC News
OL,4,Cin first stage of major cost-cutting
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,6,
OL,7,FThe cost-cutting initiative comes as
OL,8,Fministers weigh licence fee reform and
OL,9,FCharter renewal looms at the end of
OL,10,F2027.
